# Blue Nile Pearl Bracelets Review {{year}}: Every Style, Ranked by Reviews

Blue Nile's pearl bracelet collection spans 40+ styles from $210 multicolored freshwater to $2,105 diamond-clasp pieces — and right now up to 60% off clearance makes some of these the best pearl prices I've seen from any major retailer this year.

But let me tell you what this review actually is before you read it: Blue Nile is an online retailer. I have not personally worn every bracelet on this page. What I can give you that Blue Nile's own product pages can't is this: real competitor price comparisons, honest quality-tier context, a clear answer on who should NOT buy here, and every style organized by verified review count so you're not guessing which ones are actually popular. That is the review I'd want to read if I were spending $400 on a pearl bracelet for someone I care about.

### TL;DR: Blue Nile Pearl Bracelets — Farzana's Bottom Line

- **Best Overall:** [7.5" Freshwater Pearl in 14k Yellow Gold (7.0-7.5mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/75-freshwater-cultured-pearl-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-70-75mm-item-201500?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — 111 reviews, $500 — the single most-reviewed size on the page
- **Best Value:** [7.5" Freshwater in 14k Yellow Gold (6-6.5mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/75-freshwater-cultured-pearl-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-6-65mm-item-195480?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — same 111 reviews, only $400 — the 0.5mm pearl size difference is invisible on the wrist
- **Best Sale Price:** [6.5" Freshwater in 14k White Gold (6-6.5mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/65-freshwater-cultured-pearl-bracelet-in-14k-white-gold-6-65mm-item-201560?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — ~~$365~~ **$255** (30% off), 69 reviews
- **Best Specialty Style:** [Pink Freshwater Tin Cup Stationed in 14k Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/pink-freshwater-cultured-pearl-tin-cup-stationed-bracelet-in-14k-rose-gold-55mm-item-195101?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — 84 reviews, $335 — the highest-reviewed non-strand style
- **Best Premium Akoya:** [8" Classic Akoya in 18k White Gold (6.5-7.0mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-classic-akoya-cultured-pearl-bracelet-in-18k-white-gold-65-70mm-item-194698?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — ~~$1,205~~ **$843** (30% off), 18 reviews
